Body: Date: Wednesday, 20-Nov-96 20:04:38 GMT Server: NCSA/1.3 MIME-version: 1.0 Content-type: text/html Last-modified: Thursday, 07-Nov-96 19:41:15 GMT Content-length: 7148 CASHMERe Home Page Coherence Algorithms for SHared MEmory aRchitectures The CASHMERe Project Overview People Papers Overview CASHMERe stands for "Coherence Algorithms for SHared MEmory aRchitectures" and is an ongoing effort to provide efficient, scalable, shared memory with minimal hardware support.
